brew install mosquitto

If the validation required between the MqttClient and Mosquitto Server then
Mqtt Broker to Client validation through username and password
Configure in mosquitto.conf
allow_anonymous false
password_file /usr/local/etc/mosquitto/pwdfile.txt

mosquitto_passwd -c pwdfile.txt username
password and Reenter password

brew services
brew services stop mosquitto
brew services start mosquitto
